{
  "__inputs": [
    {
      "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
      "label": "Prometheus",
      "description": "Prometheus datasource for Sergeant server metrics",
      "type": "datasource",
      "pluginId": "prometheus",
      "pluginName": "Prometheus"
    }
  ],
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": { "type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --" },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  },
  "description": "Sergeant Ops home — єдина точка входу: кнопки переходу в інші сервіси (Sentry / PostHog / Coolify / Vercel) + ключові живі KPI здоров'я. Зроби стартовим дашбордом (Star → Set as home).",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [
    {
      "title": "Sentry · API (бекенд)",
      "type": "link",
      "icon": "bolt",
      "url": "https://dima-dk.sentry.io/issues/?project=4511311028879440",
      "targetBlank": true,
      "tooltip": "Помилки/краші бекенду + stack trace"
    },
    {
      "title": "Sentry · Web (фронтенд)",
      "type": "link",
      "icon": "bolt",
      "url": "https://dima-dk.sentry.io/issues/?project=4511311094480976",
      "targetBlank": true,
      "tooltip": "Помилки/краші web + session replay"
    },
    {
      "title": "PostHog — поведінка юзерів",
      "type": "link",
      "icon": "external link",
      "url": "https://eu.posthog.com/project/167740",
      "targetBlank": true,
      "tooltip": "Events, воронки, скільки активних"
    },
    {
      "title": "Coolify — бекенд/БД/деплой",
      "type": "link",
      "icon": "cloud",
      "url": "http://167.233.98.92:8000",
      "targetBlank": true,
      "tooltip": "API, Postgres, Redis, env, деплої (Hetzner + Coolify)"
    },
    {
      "title": "Vercel — фронтенд",
      "type": "link",
      "icon": "external link",
      "url": "https://vercel.com/skords-01s-projects/sergeant",
      "targetBlank": true,
      "tooltip": "Web build, preview, web env"
    },
    {
      "title": "Усі дашборди Sergeant",
      "type": "dashboards",
      "icon": "dashboard",
      "tags": ["sergeant"],
      "asDropdown": true,
      "includeVars": false,
      "targetBlank": false
    }
  ],
  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## 🧭 Куди йти за чим\n\n| Твоє питання | Сервіс (відкрий) |\n| --- | --- |\n| Метрики · логи · алерти (повільно? витрати? сигналки?) | **Grafana** — ти вже тут ↓ |\n| Що зламалось? (stack trace, краш у юзера) | **[Sentry · API ↗](https://dima-dk.sentry.io/issues/?project=4511311028879440)** · **[Web ↗](https://dima-dk.sentry.io/issues/?project=4511311094480976)** |\n| Скільки людей · де відвалюються (воронки) | **[PostHog ↗](https://eu.posthog.com/project/167740)** |\n| Деплой бекенду · Postgres · env-змінні | **[Coolify ↗](http://167.233.98.92:8000)** |\n| Деплой фронтенду · web build · preview | **[Vercel ↗](https://vercel.com/skords-01s-projects/sergeant)** |\n\n> Кнопки переходу також угорі дашборда (панель **Links** ☝️). Логи — у Grafana зліва: **Explore → Loki**."
      },
      "title": "Швидка навігація",
      "type": "text",
      "transparent": false
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
      "id": 100,
      "title": "Здоров'я зараз",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "description": "1 = обидва scrape-targets (sergeant-server + n8n) живі. 0 = хоч один впав.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": { "1": { "text": "Все живе", "color": "green" } }
            },
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": { "0": { "text": "TARGET DOWN", "color": "red" } }
            }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 7 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "title": "Scrape-targets",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "min(up{project=\"sergeant\"})",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "description": "Частка 5xx за 5хв (SLI для HTTP availability SLO 99%). Зелено < 1%.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0.01 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 7 },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "title": "HTTP 5xx ratio (SLO 99%)",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{status=~\"5..\"}[5m])) / clamp_min(sum(rate(http_requests_total[5m])), 1)",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "description": "p95 латентність non-AI маршрутів. SLO < 1000ms.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 1000 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "ms"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 7 },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "title": "p95 latency non-AI (SLO < 1s)",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(http_request_duration_ms_bucket{path!~\"/api/(chat|coach|weekly-digest|nutrition/.*)\"}[5m])))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "description": "Оцінені витрати на AI-провайдерів за останні 24 години (нижня межа — unknown-моделі не рахуються).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 2 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 5 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "decimals": 2
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 7 },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "title": "AI-витрати / 24год",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum(increase(ai_cost_estimate_usd_total[24h]))",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "description": "Трафік (req/s) по модулях + сумарний 5xx.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisLabel": "req/s",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 15,
            "lineInterpolation": "smooth",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" }
          },
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "5xx (усі)" },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "color",
                "value": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" }
              },
              { "id": "custom.lineWidth", "value": 2 }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "id": 6,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": ["mean", "max"],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "title": "Трафік по модулях + 5xx",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum by (module) (rate(http_requests_total[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ module }}",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{status=~\"5..\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "5xx (усі)",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "description": "Оцінена вартість AI ($/год) по endpoint — видно, що 'з'їдає' бюджет.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisLabel": "$/год",
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 60,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "normal" }
          },
          "unit": "currencyUSD"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 12 },
      "id": 7,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": ["mean", "max"],
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "title": "AI-витрати по endpoint ($/год)",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum by (endpoint) (rate(ai_cost_estimate_usd_total[$__rate_interval]) * 3600)",
          "legendFormat": "{{ endpoint }}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 20 },
      "id": 101,
      "title": "Опорні сигнали",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "description": "Активні (checked-out) з'єднання з Postgres. Якщо постійно високо + waiting > 0 — pool saturate.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 8 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 21 },
      "id": 8,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "title": "DB активні з'єднання",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum(db_pool_size_current{state=\"active\"})",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "description": "Клієнти в черзі за з'єднанням. У нормі 0; стабільно > 0 = бекенд впирається в БД.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 1 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 21 },
      "id": 9,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "title": "DB черга (waiting)",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum(db_pool_size_current{state=\"waiting\"})",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "description": "AI-запити за секунду по outcome (ok/error/rate_limited/timeout).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisLabel": "req/s",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 15,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" }
          },
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 21 },
      "id": 10,
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "calcs": ["mean"],
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "right"
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "title": "AI-запити по outcome",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum by (outcome) (rate(ai_requests_total[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ outcome }}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "type": "timeseries"
    }
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "tags": ["sergeant", "home", "ops"],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "current": {
          "selected": false,
          "text": "Prometheus",
          "value": "Prometheus"
        },
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": false,
        "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
        "options": [],
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "type": "datasource"
      }
    ]
  },
  "time": { "from": "now-6h", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "Europe/Kyiv",
  "title": "Sergeant — Ops Home",
  "uid": "sergeant-ops-home",
  "version": 1
}
